[32m│[0m ## Detailed Summary                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I executed systematic SSTI payload testing against Twig v1.19.0 at           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m http://127.0.0.1:8080/index.php. The testing confirms a working Server-Side  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Template Injection vulnerability with successful expression evaluation.      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Test Results:**                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ **Basic Math ({{7*7}})**: Successfully evaluated to "49", confirming    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m SSTI vulnerability                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ **_context Array ({{_context}})**: Array accessible with string         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m conversion warning                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ⚠️ **_self Object Traversal**: Objects cause fatal errors when converted to [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m string, indicating object access is possible but requires proper method      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m invocation                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Confirmed Twig v1.19.0 with core, escaper, and optimizer extensions loaded [32m│[0m
